        "new_string": "// NewProvider creates a new TracerProvider configured for Flipt tracing.\n// If tracingCfg is nil, defaults to AlwaysSample (1.0 sampling rate).\nfunc NewProvider(ctx context.Context, fliptVersion string, tracingCfg *config.TracingConfig) (*tracesdk.TracerProvider, error) {\n\ttraceResource, err := newResource(ctx, fliptVersion)\n\tif err != nil {\n\t\treturn nil, err\n\t}\n\n\tvar sampler tracesdk.Sampler\n\tif tracingCfg != nil {\n\t\tsampler = tracesdk.ParentBased(\n\t\t\ttracesdk.TraceIDRatioBased(tracingCfg.SamplingRate),\n\t\t)\n\t} else {\n\t\tsampler = tracesdk.AlwaysSample()\n\t}\n\n\treturn tracesdk.NewTracerProvider(\n\t\ttracesdk.WithResource(traceResource),\n\t\ttracesdk.WithSampler(sampler),\n\t), nil\n}",
